SET
    course_description = '<div class="richtext richtext__medium"> <div class="lede">Are you ready to take on the world of global business leadership?</div><p>The Master of Business Administration (Global) is your gateway to thrive in today''s fast-paced business world. Dive into critical thinking, where you''ll gain a deeper understanding of how businesses evolve. Fuel your creativity by challenging traditional norms and creating innovative solutions for modern organisations.</p><p>Ethics are at our core. You''ll learn to lead with integrity across all sectors, including private, public, and social enterprises, shaping ethical perspectives that guide your management approach. We get you ready for management roles with the expertise to drive success.</p><p>Ready to inspire and guide others? Start your MBA journey now to shape the future of business.</p><p>For international students studying at our <a href="https://www.utas.edu.au/community-and-partners/partner/educational/melbourne">Melbourne study centre</a> and <a href="https://www.utas.edu.au/community-and-partners/partner/international/ultimo" title="Ultimo study centre">Ultimo study centre</a>, the following specialisations are available: Finance, and Marketing.</p><hr/> </div>',
